                <mxCell id="79" value="$$ \mathrm{Flip}(\%) \;=\; 100 \cdot \frac{1}{N}\sum_{i=1}^{N}\mathbf{1}\!\left[\;\mathbf{1}\!\left(p^{(i)}_{y}&amp;gt;\tau\right)\neq \mathbf{1}\!\left(\tilde p^{(i)}_{y}&amp;gt;\tau\right)\;\right] $$&amp;nbsp; $$ \mathrm{Mean\ L1} \;=\; \frac{1}{N}\sum_{i=1}^{N}\left\lVert \tilde x^{(i)} - x^{(i)} \right\rVert_{1} \qquad $$&amp;nbsp; $$ \mathrm{MNAC} \;=\; \frac{1}{N}\sum_{i=1}^{N}\;\sum_{k\neq y}\mathbf{1}\!\left[\;\mathbf{1}\!\left(p^{(i)}_{k}&amp;gt;\tau\right)\neq \mathbf{1}\!\left(\tilde p^{(i)}_{k}&amp;gt;\tau\right)\;\right] $$&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=9;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="72.78" y="458" width="227.22" height="30" as="geometry"/>
